      "writtenOn": "2021-05-26T22:47:45Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I think we don\u0027t want to import the same package twice. Also if there is an alias, then probably there is a reason for it (maybe there is another package with errors name)\n\nI think we even should fail if someone import errors as \".\" or \"_\". For now, maybe ignore such files?",
